definitions.definition: An evergreen coniferous tree with flattened shoots bearing small scale-like leaves, whose dark foliage is sometimes associated with mourning , in family Cupressaceae , especially the genera Cupressus and Chamaecyparis .

main_definition: An evergreen coniferous tree with flattened shoots bearing small scale-like leaves, whose dark foliage is sometimes associated with mourning , in family Cupressaceae , especially the genera Cupressus and Chamaecyparis .
